  - q: "Why is Nairobi a good base for a chief of staff serving all of Africa?"
    a: "Nairobi is East Africa's largest commercial and tech hub, with direct flights and strong connectivity across the continent, a deep operations talent pool built over fifteen years of BPO and fintech growth, and a timezone (EAT, UTC+3) that overlaps with both African markets and, unusually, Europe and the US East Coast in the same working day."
